"##############################
" Symbols
" NOTE: ga (get ascii) to get unicode value.
" NOTE: Input special symbol, Ctrl+v -> u[unicode].
" Font patch, https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts
" set powerline symbols (test ,)
